{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"If you go on the TED website,"},{"time":4000,"text":"you can currently find there"},{"time":6000,"text":"over a full week of TEDTalk videos,"},{"time":9000,"text":"over 1.3 million"},{"time":11000,"text":"words of transcripts"},{"time":13000,"text":"and millions of user ratings."},{"time":15000,"text":"And that's a huge amount of data."},{"time":18000,"text":"And it got me wondering:"},{"time":20000,"text":"If you took all this data"},{"time":22000,"text":"and put it through statistical analysis,"},{"time":24000,"text":"could you reverse engineer a TEDTalk?"},{"time":26000,"text":"Could you create"},{"time":28000,"text":"the ultimate TEDTalk?"},{"time":30000,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":32000,"text":"And also, could you create"},{"time":34000,"text":"the worst possible TEDTalk"},{"time":36000,"text":"that they would still let you get away with?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"To find this out, I looked at three things:"},{"time":40000,"text":"I looked at the topic that you should choose,"},{"time":42000,"text":"I looked at how you should deliver it"},{"time":45000,"text":"and the visuals onstage."},{"time":47000,"text":"Now, with the topic: There's a whole range of topics you can choose,"},{"time":50000,"text":"but you should choose wisely,"},{"time":52000,"text":"because your topic strongly correlates"},{"time":54000,"text":"with how users will react to your talk."},{"time":57000,"text":"Now, to make this more concrete,"},{"time":59000,"text":"let's look at the list of top 10 words"},{"time":62000,"text":"that statistically stick out"},{"time":64000,"text":"in the most favorite TEDTalks"},{"time":66000,"text":"and in the least favorite TEDTalks."},{"time":69000,"text":"So if you came here"},{"time":71000,"text":"to talk about how French coffee"},{"time":73000,"text":"will spread happiness in our brains,"},{"time":76000,"text":"that's a go."},{"time":78000,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":80000,"text":"Whereas, if you wanted to talk about"},{"time":82000,"text":"your project involving"},{"time":84000,"text":"oxygen, girls, aircraft --"},{"time":86000,"text":"actually, I would like to hear that talk, (Laughter)"},{"time":88000,"text":"but statistics say it's not so good."},{"time":90000,"text":"Oh, well."},{"time":92000,"text":"If you generalize this,"},{"time":94000,"text":"the most favorite TEDTalks are those"},{"time":96000,"text":"that feature topics we can connect with,"},{"time":99000,"text":"both easily and deeply,"},{"time":101000,"text":"such as happiness, our own body,"},{"time":103000,"text":"food, emotions."},{"time":105000,"text":"And the more technical topics,"},{"time":107000,"text":"such as architecture, materials and, strangely enough, men,"},{"time":110000,"text":"those are not good topics to talk about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113000,"text":"How should you deliver your talk?"},{"time":115000,"text":"TED is famous for keeping"},{"time":117000,"text":"a very sharp eye on the clock,"},{"time":119000,"text":"so they're going to hate me"},{"time":121000,"text":"for revealing this, because, actually,"},{"time":123000,"text":"you should talk as long as they will let you. (Laughter)"},{"time":125000,"text":"Because the most favorite TEDTalks"},{"time":128000,"text":"are, on average, over 50 percent longer"},{"time":130000,"text":"than the least favorite ones."},{"time":133000,"text":"And this holds true for all ranking lists on TED.com"},{"time":135000,"text":"except if you want to have a talk"},{"time":137000,"text":"that's beautiful, inspiring or funny."},{"time":139000,"text":"Then, you should be brief. (Laughter) But other than that,"},{"time":141000,"text":"talk until they drag you off the stage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"Now, while ..."},{"time":148000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":154000,"text":"While you're pushing the clock, there's a few rules to obey."},{"time":157000,"text":"I found these rules out by comparing the statistics"},{"time":159000,"text":"of four-word phrases"},{"time":161000,"text":"that appear more often in the most favorite TEDTalks"},{"time":164000,"text":"as opposed to the least favorite TEDTalks."},{"time":166000,"text":"I'll give you three examples."},{"time":168000,"text":"First of all, I must, as a speaker,"},{"time":170000,"text":"provide a service to the audience and talk about what I will give you,"},{"time":173000,"text":"instead of saying what I can't have."},{"time":175000,"text":"Secondly, it's imperative"},{"time":177000,"text":"that you do not cite The New York Times."},{"time":179000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":181000,"text":"And finally, it's okay for the speaker -- that's the good news --"},{"time":184000,"text":"to fake intellectual capacity."},{"time":186000,"text":"If I don't understand something, I can just say, \"etc., etc.\""},{"time":189000,"text":"You'll all stay with me."},{"time":191000,"text":"It's perfectly fine."},{"time":193000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"Now, let's go to the visuals."},{"time":199000,"text":"The most obvious visual thing on stage is the speaker."},{"time":202000,"text":"And analysis shows if you want to be"},{"time":204000,"text":"among the most favorite TED speakers,"},{"time":206000,"text":"you should let your hair grow a little bit longer than average,"},{"time":209000,"text":"make sure you wear your glasses and be slightly more dressed-up"},{"time":212000,"text":"than the average TED speaker."},{"time":214000,"text":"Slides are okay, though you might consider going for props."},{"time":217000,"text":"And now the most important thing,"},{"time":219000,"text":"that is the mood onstage."},{"time":221000,"text":"Color plays a very important role."},{"time":223000,"text":"Color closely correlates"},{"time":225000,"text":"with the ratings that talks get on the website."},{"time":228000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":230000,"text":"For example, fascinating talks"},{"time":232000,"text":"contain a statistically high amount"},{"time":234000,"text":"of exactly this blue color, (Laughter)"},{"time":236000,"text":"much more than the average TEDTalk."},{"time":238000,"text":"Ingenious TEDTalks, much more this green color,"},{"time":240000,"text":"etc., et."},{"time":242000,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":249000,"text":"Now, personally, I think"},{"time":251000,"text":"I'm not the first one who has done this analysis,"},{"time":253000,"text":"but I'll leave this"},{"time":255000,"text":"to your good judgment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"So, now it's time to put it all together"},{"time":260000,"text":"and design the ultimate TEDTalk."},{"time":262000,"text":"Now, since this is TEDActive,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and I learned from my analysis"},{"time":266000,"text":"that I should actually give you something,"},{"time":268000,"text":"I will not impose the ultimate"},{"time":270000,"text":"or worst TEDTalk on you,"},{"time":272000,"text":"but rather give you a tool to create your own."},{"time":274000,"text":"And I call this tool the TEDPad."},{"time":277000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":280000,"text":"And the TEDPad is a matrix"},{"time":282000,"text":"of 100 specifically selected,"},{"time":284000,"text":"highly curated sentences"},{"time":287000,"text":"that you can easily piece together to get your own TEDTalk."},{"time":292000,"text":"You only have to make one decision,"},{"time":294000,"text":"and that is: Are you going to use the white version"},{"time":296000,"text":"for very good TEDTalks,"},{"time":298000,"text":"about creativity, human genius?"},{"time":300000,"text":"Or are you going to go with a black version,"},{"time":302000,"text":"which will allow you to create really bad TEDTalks,"},{"time":304000,"text":"mostly about blogs,"},{"time":306000,"text":"politics and stuff?"},{"time":308000,"text":"So, download it and have fun with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"Now I hope you enjoy the session."},{"time":313000,"text":"I hope you enjoy designing your own"},{"time":315000,"text":"ultimate and worst possible TEDTalks."},{"time":317000,"text":"And I hope some of you will be inspired for next year"},{"time":320000,"text":"to create this, which I really want to see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325000,"text":"(Applause) Thanks."}]}]}